{"tid":2423318,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國侯任貿易代表戴琪  支持以關稅作為抗衡中國貿易政策的合法工具","createTime":"2021-02-26T00:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T10:35:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c61833abd1856bb310c374722c025de6308aa57c","tid":2423318,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:28:09.000Z","msg":"戴琪支持以關稅作為抗衡中國貿易政策的合法工具<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577592-20210226.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577592-20210226.htm&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd60qdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=adadc0a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577592-20210226.htm&h=f1123eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577592-20210226.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登提名的貿易代表人選戴琪表示，支持以關稅作為抗衡中國貿易政策的合法工具，並<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">強調中國必須履行與上屆政府達成的第一階段貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n戴琪出席參議院金融委員會的提名聽證會時強調，關稅是美國公平貿易補救工具中非常重要的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n她形容，中國是極為強大的競爭對手，政府可直接干預經濟。美國需要以更多的戰略投資、增加供應鏈彈性和貿易執行力來應對中國的戰略和野心，她呼籲與其他國家合作，修補全球的貿易規則，消除被中國利用的灰色地帶。<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n戴琪又說，華府會探討所有可能選項，推動中國推行必要的結構改革，確保兩大經濟體之間公平競爭。"},{"pid":"ae6594eb4800a8bd8e877354b12a07aa2fae2ba5","tid":2423318,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4571656a08dbcd19f91c104686bb3faecbe26b1b","tid":2423318,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"漢奸走狗賣國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid